author: Katie Frates
title: MUST WATCH: Kellyanne Conway Doing Stand-Up Comedy
text:
5442250 
Kellyanne Conway, President Donald Trump’s special adviser, used to do stand-up comedy. 
Someone unearthed a Nov. 26, 1998 video of Conway, 31 at the time, cracking jokes and uploaded it to C-SPAN Sunday . 
They didn’t give it a very nice title, either: “ Kellyanne Terrible Kellyanne Fitzpatrick/Conway attempts comedy and makes everyone cringe.”
